snippet.description:
When I started activating parks in the @ParksOnTheAir program, I never dreamed of doing 100 activations. This video documents my 100th activation at my home park, US-10562, Port Hudson State Historic Site, in southeast Louisiana. 
@Brent_N4BDW explained to me the Eagle's Nest award in the POTA program.  Before then, I didn't even know it existed or just how special it was.
So, I knew this would be a special day out at the park, but I never realized just how special it would be. The support from the Ham community is unbelievable.  I am so blessed to have achieved this goal.
I want to thank everyone who hunted me on this special day and everyone who supports me in this hobby.
I used the @SPOOLTENNA 4010 EFHW for this activation and it performed as expected.
